Title: host: addition of show single host endpoint
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1683032836
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

Prior to this werk, the list hosts collection endpoint returned hosts
which also included a link to the respective host. Following those links
returned an error as the endpoint did not exist. This is now added
with this werk.

